<br>
Terrorism will not make the Israelis give in, nor will it make the Americans support the Palestinians.  It only hurts their cause, it does nothing to help it.  The problem is they are too stupid to realize it and think they can bully the Israelis into submission.  It isn't going to happen.  I think it would have happened already if it were going to.  All we have seen is Israel hardening its stance against them.<br>
