<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Why did he pursue Oslo then ? Why did he sign it ? Tell me, what exactly did he do in the 90's that make you believe he was against Oslo ? Again, Arafat is NOT in control of Hamas.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
