<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>That's how Hamas thinks also - Israel oppress them, almost all Israeli people support them and that's why they can justify their horrific crimes. Sure, Israel's crimes may be less horrific, but that doesn't change a thing. Innocents are victimized by both Hamas and Israel.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
