<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Palestinians won't stop supporting terrorism until Israel treats them better. It's an endless spiral of violence. Pointing fingers and placing blame is very contra-constructive, you need compromise.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
